<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10105080>
    dc:description "Figs. 10–16. Hemiosus dejeanii, third instar larva, dorsal view. 10) head capsule; 11) clypeolabrum; 12) left mandible; 13) right mandible; 14) right antenna; 15) right maxilla; 16) labium. Scale bars: Figures 10 ¼ 0.2 mm, Figures 11–16 ¼ 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10105080/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

